== 설치 ==

== 하드웨어 감지 ==

To choose the right driver, first detect the used storage controller. [[Hardware detection|lspci]] can be used for this task:

{{RootCmd|lspci {{!}} grep --color -E "IDE{{!}}SATA"}}

